{"tid":2134270,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發時空．沈旭暉 013】「DQ邏輯」與香港的未來","createTime":"2020-07-31T14:49:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T02:43:34.000Z","uid":198,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"88fae577344b083c4e8e4fa0d895724a99427548","tid":2134270,"uid":198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:49:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sj7GWc1EzII\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dsj7GWc1EzII&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOfjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=c66e3f0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sj7GWc1EzII</a><br />\n<br />\n根據北京理解，香港特區政府自然要完全按照中央政府的意思去管治香港，向有監督權的兩辦匯報。而香港特區政府本身，也必須行政主導一切，任何屬於制度內的存在，都不能挑戰行政主導這原則，無論是立法機關、司法機關、公務員工會還是區議會，因為香港制度內毋需要任何制衡，一切都要回歸「民主集中制」基本點。以上這條真正的紅線，才是現在的DQ線。至於說出來的原因：甚麼支持國際制裁、原則上反對國安法、無條件否決財政預算案等，都是虛線。而北京對非建制陣營傳達的訊號，亦清晰不過。"},{"pid":"efc35906a699074102962cbf9a179efa1cb36ade","tid":2134270,"uid":198,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:50:36.000Z","msg":"其實都係佢篇文講既野 不過Youtube再講多次 再 詳細D<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d994d599acbadabc5130dda99ee02037691739e","tid":2134270,"uid":198,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:50:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f36967805bf64ac1cd3e522b75f5fe286768630d","tid":2134270,"uid":198,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:51:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />